.TH crypt_bsdbf 5 "13 Sep 2009" "SunOS 5.11" "Standards, Environments, and Macros"
.SH NAME
crypt_bsdbf \- password hashing module using Blowfish cryptographic
algorithm
.SH SYNOPSIS
.LP
.nf
\fB/usr/lib/security/$ISA/crypt_bsdbf.so\fR
.fi

.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
.LP
The
.B crypt_bsdbf
module is a one-way password hashing module for use
with
.BR crypt (3C)
that uses the Blowfish cryptographic algorithm. The
algorithm identifier for
.BR crypt.conf (4)
and
.BR policy.conf (4)
is
.BR 2a .
.sp
.LP
The maximum password length for
.B crypt_bsdbf
is 72 characters.
